, 'This gigantic military installation is the pride of the Amarr Navy. Thousands, sometimes hundreds of thousands, of slaves pour their blood, sweat and tears into erecting one of these mega-structures. Only a fool would attempt to assault such a massive base without a fleet behind him.\r\n\r\nDocking has been prohibited into this station without proper authorization.', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '4', '0', '0'), ('26122', '526', 'Pillaging 101', 'This informative brochure contains helpful diagrams and elaborate tutorials on how to effectively function as a successful brigand. Key chapters include:<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPriority Pillaging – Triage style tactics for post-combat logistics<br>\r\nPursuing Passersby – Why anonymity is more useful than infamy<br>\r\nPunishing Pirates – What to do with a drunken crewman early in the morning<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThis handy guide could turn even the noblest capsuleer into a ruthless raider in just a few short years of night courses.\r\n', '34_06', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26123', '526', 'The Little Pirate That Could', 'Inspirational story if there ever was one. Fills every pirate wannabe with pride.', '34_06', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26124', '526', '17 Successful Torture Techniques', 'You can only wonder about the dedication in filtering the successful techniques from the unsuccessful ones.', '34_06', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26125', '526', 'Test Bong', 'A curious device used by pirates to test their own product. Seems heavily used.', '11_04', '100', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26126', '526', 'Flower Power Powder', 'Oddly smelling powder presumably used by pirates in some of their more exotic formulas.', '10_06', '1000', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26127', '526', 'Angel Cartel Dust', 'Finely grained dust manufactured by the Angel Cartel for use in hallucination drugs.', '10_06', '1000', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26128', '370', 'Sansha Infiltrator Tag', 'A dogtag carried by members of the Sansha''s navy. Members carrying the rank of infiltrator are often tasked with intercepting and deciphering enemy communications.', '43_05', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26129', '526', 'Cold Turkey', 'From what little information you can garner the pirates seemed severely afraid of encountering cold turkeys and were researching ways to counter them. Why frozen poultry would frighten space pirates so is anybody''s guess.', '06_13', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26130', '820', 'Sansha Infiltrator', 'Revelling in the symbiotic relationship of man and machine Sansha''s Commanders can push themselves harder and further than others. Sansha Infiltrators are often tasked with intercepting and deciphering enemy communications.', '', '10010000', '100100', '235', '1', '4', '0', '0'), ('26131', '526', 'Booster Pack', 'Apparently the pirates were researching a pack to store drugs in. It''s supposed to have 11 racks, one for strong boosters, three for improved boosters and seven for standard boosters. What a curious idea. ', '34_07', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26132', '526', 'Purple Haze', 'Purple haze is apparently a nirvana-like state that all pirates dream of entering, yet one that can kill the uninitiated. From the pieces of research notes you have here it seems the pirates sought to prolong this euphoric state while minimizing the risks of entering it. ', '11_07', '1', '0.1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26135', '306', 'Production Cache', 'A locked storage bin containing various items used by the local pirates in their drug manufacturing. A bit of hacking might unlock it.', '26_11', '10000', '27500', '2700', '1', '0', '0', '0'), ('26136', '306', 'Training Cube', 'The training cube is used by the local pirates to learn how to become good pirates. It is password protected, but probably not all that well.', '', '10000', '27500', '2700', '1', '1', '0', '0'), ('26137', '306', 'Research Lab', 'The local pirates are actively trying to enha